### Reasoning Language Model (RLM) Endpoint — Request Payloads
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Endpoint:  POST /rlm/chat/completions
###
### Notes:
### - The RLM endpoint accepts the SAME ChatCompletionRequest schema
###   as /v1/chat/completions and /dspy/chat/completions.
### - It runs DSPy ReAct under the hood, but always forwards
###   `reasoning_effort` to the underlying LM (via OpenRouter's
###   unified `reasoning` field).
### - `reasoning_effort` may be "low" | "medium" | "high".
###   When omitted, the server defaults to "medium".
### - Use a reasoning-capable model (o-series, deepseek-r1,
###   gpt-5-thinking, claude-thinking, etc.). Non-reasoning models
###   simply ignore the field upstream.
### - Tools (weather, email) are loaded server-side from the tool
###   registry — you do NOT need to pass `tools` in the body. The
###   `tools` / `tool_choice` fields are accepted by the schema but
###   ignored by the route (scenarios 8a–8d below show the field
###   structure for reference and to confirm the request still
###   validates with them present).
### ============================================================


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1a. Default reasoning_effort (omitted → "medium") — Non-Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is 17 multiplied by 23? Show your reasoning briefly."
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1b. Default reasoning_effort (omitted → "medium") — Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is 17 multiplied by 23? Show your reasoning briefly."
    }
  ],
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2a. effort=low — Non-Streaming
### Cheapest reasoning budget. Good for short, well-scoped questions.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Briefly: is 31337 a prime number?"
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "low"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2b. effort=low — Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Briefly: is 31337 a prime number?"
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "low",
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3a. effort=medium — Non-Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "deepseek/deepseek-r1",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Plan a 3-step approach for caching reasoning-model responses without leaking PII."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "medium"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3b. effort=medium — Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "deepseek/deepseek-r1",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Plan a 3-step approach for caching reasoning-model responses without leaking PII."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "medium",
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4a. effort=high — Non-Streaming
### Heavy reasoning budget. Good for multi-step word problems.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Three friends split a $173 bill with an 18% tip and one of them paid $80 in cash. How much do the other two each owe? Show your reasoning briefly."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4b. effort=high — Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Three friends split a $173 bill with an 18% tip and one of them paid $80 in cash. How much do the other two each owe? Show your reasoning briefly."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high",
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5a. Tool Use — Weather + Reasoning (Non-Streaming)
### Agent should pick the weather tool then reason over the result.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Mumbai. Based on the result, decide if it's a good day for outdoor cricket and explain why."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "medium"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5b. Tool Use — Weather + Reasoning (Streaming)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Mumbai. Based on the result, decide if it's a good day for outdoor cricket and explain why."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "medium",
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6a. Multi-Tool + Reasoning — Non-Streaming
### Weather + email, with the model reasoning about both steps.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Ahmedabad, then draft a casual email to team@company.com suggesting whether tomorrow is a good day for an outdoor team lunch. Justify your suggestion."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6b. Multi-Tool + Reasoning — Streaming
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Ahmedabad, then draft a casual email to team@company.com suggesting whether tomorrow is a good day for an outdoor team lunch. Justify your suggestion."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high",
  "stream": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Model with explicit openrouter/ prefix — Non-Streaming
### `openrouter/` prefix is added automatically by normalize_model()
### but the explicit form should also work.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openrouter/openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Briefly: which is heavier, 1 kg of feathers or 1 kg of steel? Explain."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "low"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8a. Request with `tools` specified — Weather only
### NOTE: the agent picks tools from the SERVER-SIDE registry; the
### `tools` / `tool_choice` fields here are accepted-but-ignored.
### Useful for confirming OpenAI-shaped requests still validate.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the weather in Bengaluru? Recommend an outfit based on it."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "medium",
  "tool_choice": "auto",
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_weather",
        "description": "Get current weather information for a given city",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "city": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The city name to get weather for"
            }
          },
          "required": ["city"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8b. Request with `tools` specified — Email only (Streaming)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Draft a polite email to client@example.com explaining that the deliverable is delayed by two days, and justify the delay tactfully."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high",
  "stream": true,
  "tool_choice": "auto",
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "generate_email",
        "description": "Generate a formatted email with the given recipient, subject, and optional tone",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "to": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email recipient address"
            },
            "subject": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email subject line"
            },
            "tone": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Tone of the email (e.g. formal, casual)",
              "default": "formal"
            }
          },
          "required": ["to", "subject"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8c. Full Payload — Both tools, all schema fields, Non-Streaming
### Mirrors how an OpenAI SDK client would send a tool-using request.
### `temperature`, `max_tokens`, etc. are accepted but ignored.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant that uses tools when appropriate."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Jaipur, then email a one-line summary to manager@company.com with the subject 'Jaipur weather'."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high",
  "stream": false,
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 500,
  "top_p": 0.9,
  "frequency_penalty": 0.2,
  "presence_penalty": 0.1,
  "stop": ["END"],
  "tool_choice": "auto",
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_weather",
        "description": "Get current weather information for a given city",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "city": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The city name to get weather for"
            }
          },
          "required": ["city"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "generate_email",
        "description": "Generate a formatted email with the given recipient, subject, and optional tone",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "to": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email recipient address"
            },
            "subject": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email subject line"
            },
            "tone": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Tone of the email (e.g. formal, casual)",
              "default": "formal"
            }
          },
          "required": ["to", "subject"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8d. Full Payload — Both tools, Streaming
### Same body shape as 8c, but with stream=true.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant that uses tools when appropriate."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Check the weather in Jaipur, then email a one-line summary to manager@company.com with the subject 'Jaipur weather'."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "high",
  "stream": true,
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 500,
  "top_p": 0.9,
  "frequency_penalty": 0.2,
  "presence_penalty": 0.1,
  "stop": ["END"],
  "tool_choice": "auto",
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_weather",
        "description": "Get current weather information for a given city",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "city": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The city name to get weather for"
            }
          },
          "required": ["city"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "generate_email",
        "description": "Generate a formatted email with the given recipient, subject, and optional tone",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "to": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email recipient address"
            },
            "subject": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Email subject line"
            },
            "tone": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Tone of the email (e.g. formal, casual)",
              "default": "formal"
            }
          },
          "required": ["to", "subject"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Auth Header Example (only needed if PROXY_API_KEY is set)
### Uncomment Authorization line on a server with auth enabled.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST http://localhost:8000/rlm/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer your-proxy-api-key-here

{
  "model": "openai/o4-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Ping."
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_effort": "low"
}
